'''Brutal blue dragons''' are found in the north-west section in the [[Catacombs of Kourend]]. They are currently the only monster to drop the [[blue d'hide body]] (an item rarely required for medium and hard emote [[clues]]).

Like all [[brutal dragon]]s, they use [[melee]], [[magic]] and long-range [[dragonfire]]. Using both [[Protect from Magic]] and [[Antifire potion]] will  completely protect players from damage, if players don't stand in melee range. Note: An Anti-dragon shield with Protect from Magic will still cause you to take a small amount of dragonfire damage.

